  NOTES:
   Use target="_blank" only when sending visitors off-site to pages related to our website.
   example:
   Our Page > Our Facebook Page = target="_blank"
   Our Page > Another website = no target declaration set

   In some instances, it may make sense to use rel="nofollow" when linking to certain external & internal pages.
